{"tid":1379383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果聽日林鄭下台...","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T19:19:09.000Z","uid":260903,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7fe394053b4585bb94eb534728f1acb5e50a3fe","tid":1379383,"uid":260903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:58:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不妥協！</span></span><br />\n就算加多樣獨立調查委員會，唔講獨立性成疑，查都要查一大輪，之後嘅訴求又可以hea過。<br />\n<br />\n冇真普選，林鄭做，張建宗做，<span style=\"color: red;\">邊撚個做都一撚樣！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">堅持五大訴求！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多人都唔夠堅持五大訴求，甚至噏唔出係乜。有見及此，小弟整左個六字版本，希望易記易上口，嗌出嚟亦都有氣勢啲：<br />\n<br />\n1. 完全撤回修例<br />\n2. 收回暴動定性<br />\n3. 撤銷義士控罪<br />\n4. 獨立調查警隊<br />\n5. 實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/THfOzOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTHfOzOv.png&h=f9aadfd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFAu3GR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFAu3GR.png&h=cc0f688e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ca88c6ef07f74156c9c98173734a8e6b8dabe7a","tid":1379383,"uid":146865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:59:38.000Z","msg":"［推上熱門］推翻暴政就係需要不斷地進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推小弟感激不盡🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"e57a80082a085916f50a01492edd2a865106a179","tid":1379383,"uid":260903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c1544f0c989dacdfa9c8e2c9e753b7c983209e","tid":1379383,"uid":276660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:10:27.000Z","msg":"我要雙普選"},{"pid":"2b223a88216eaf9b6e7fb0f055b56b1a1662274f","tid":1379383,"uid":260903